@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title ServiceAccount Token pour Image Pull (K8s 1.34 Beta)

skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor<<pod>> #90EE90
  BackgroundColor<<registry>> #87CEEB
  BackgroundColor<<secret>> #FFB6C1
  BackgroundColor<<token>> #FFEFD5
}

rectangle "Avant: Image Pull Secrets" as before {
  rectangle "Pod" as pod1 <<pod>>
  rectangle "imagePullSecrets\n(long-lived)" as secret <<secret>>
  rectangle "Container\nRegistry" as reg1 <<registry>>

  pod1 -right-> secret : reference
  secret -right-> reg1 : credentials statiques

  note bottom of secret
    **Problemes:**
    - Secret long-lived
    - Rotation manuelle
    - Partage entre pods
    - Risque de fuite
  end note
}

rectangle "Apres: SA Token Auth" as after {
  rectangle "Pod" as pod2 <<pod>>
  rectangle "ServiceAccount\nToken (short-lived)" as token <<token>>
  rectangle "Container\nRegistry" as reg2 <<registry>>

  pod2 -right-> token : auto-generated
  token -right-> reg2 : JWT ephemere

  note bottom of token
    **Avantages:**
    - Token ephemere (~1h)
    - Rotation automatique
    - Scope par Pod
    - Pas de secret a gerer
  end note
}

note right of after
  **Configuration:**
  ```yaml
  apiVersion: v1
  kind: Pod
  spec:
    serviceAccountName: my-sa
    containers:
    - image: registry.io/app:v1
  ```

  Le kubelet utilise le SA token
  pour s'authentifier au registry
end note

legend right
  |= Methode |= Duree vie |= Rotation |= Securite |
  | imagePullSecrets | Illimitee | Manuelle | Faible |
  | **SA Token** | **~1h** | **Auto** | **Forte** |
endlegend

footer **KEP-4412:** Authentification registry sans secrets long-lived
@enduml
